# Deployment Guide — Streamlit Cloud

1. Go to https://share.streamlit.io or https://streamlit.io/cloud
2. Sign in using your GitHub account.
3. Click “New app”.
4. Connect your GitHub repository or upload this folder as a repo.
5. Set entry point as app.py
6. Streamlit Cloud will automatically install dependencies.
7. Once deployed, you’ll get a live URL like:
   https://yourname-loan-predictor.streamlit.app
